channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: Blatant Antisemitism: France Bans Israel From Defense Show- But Still Boasts 'Trophy' Israeli Tank
Biden announces sweeping protections for migrant spouses of US citizens
item.description: President Biden is announcing sweeping new rules that would protect the immigration status of hundreds of thousands of family members of current U.S. citizens.

item.title: Melania Trump to Host 2nd Event With Log Cabin Republicans
item.description: Former first lady Melania Trump is expected to headline an event for the Log Cabin Republicans next month at Trump Tower in New York, Politico reported Monday.

item.title: RECEIPTS PROVIDED: Email Exchange Reveals Thuggery of Gavin Newsom's Chief of Staff
Chicago Teachers Union president raises eyebrows with claims about conservatives
item.description: Chicago Teachers Union President Stacy Davis Gates told a radio station host that conservatives do not want Black children to be able to read.

item.title: House Republicans Seek to Overhaul NIH
item.description: Congressional Republicans are rolling out plans to reorganize the National Institutes of Health (NIH) and remove its authority from commissioning risky gain of function research and halt such experiments until new reforms are established, Axios reported Monday.

item.title: Bill Ackman, Piers Morgan Sound Alarm on Biden's Issues While Mark Cuban Defends Him
'Squad' lawmaker in danger of losing primary as Dem-led attacks pile up
item.description: Rep. Jamaal Bowman is facing pressure from members of his own party as his anti-Israel stance throws his re-election bid into uncertainty.

item.title: Black Farmers Look to Trump for Economic Support
item.description: Black farmers in Georgia are turning to Donald Trump for economic solutions and rejecting Joe Biden's economic policies.

item.title: Trump targets House Freedom Caucus chair in intra-party Republican primary feud
item.description: House Freedom Caucus chair Republican Rep. Bob Good is being targeted by former President Trump as he runs for re-election, as Virginia and Oklahoma hold primaries on Tuesday

item.title: Russia-NKorea Military Alliance 'Great Concern' to US
item.description: The Biden administration said Monday that Russia's deepening military alliance with North Korea is of "great concern."

item.title: Joe Biden's America: Secret Service Agent Robbed During President's California Visit
Top Republican demands answers after WH protests yield 0 arrests; questions 'political sympathy' with vandals
item.description: A top Republican senator called for the Interior Department to answer for the lack of arrest and accountability for the pro-Palestinian violence that erupted near the White House.

item.title: Secret Service Agent Robbed at Gunpoint in Calif.
item.description: An off-duty U.S. Secret Service agent was robbed at gunpoint over the weekend in Tustin, California, while President Joe Biden was in Los Angeles for a star-studded fundraiser, local and federal law enforcement announced Monday.
